Expand description

AVStreamGroupTileGrid holds information on how to combine several independent images on a single canvas for presentation.

The output should be a @ref AVStreamGroupTileGrid.background â€œbackgroundâ€ colored @ref AVStreamGroupTileGrid.coded_width â€œcoded_widthâ€ x @ref AVStreamGroupTileGrid.coded_height â€œcoded_heightâ€ canvas where a @ref AVStreamGroupTileGrid.nb_tiles â€œnb_tilesâ€ amount of tiles are placed in the order they appear in the @ref AVStreamGroupTileGrid.offsets â€œoffsetsâ€ array, at the exact offset described for them. In particular, if two or more tiles overlap, the image with higher index in the @ref AVStreamGroupTileGrid.offsets â€œoffsetsâ€ array takes priority. Note that a single image may be used multiple times, i.e. multiple entries in @ref AVStreamGroupTileGrid.offsets â€œoffsetsâ€ may have the same value of idx.

The following is an example of a simple grid with 3 rows and 4 columns:

Assuming all tiles have a dimension of 512x512, the @ref AVStreamGroupTileGrid.offsets â€œoffsetâ€ of the topleft pixel of the first @ref AVStreamGroup.streams â€œstreamâ€ in the group is â€œ0,0â€, the @ref AVStreamGroupTileGrid.offsets â€œoffsetâ€ of the topleft pixel of the second @ref AVStreamGroup.streams â€œstreamâ€ in the group is â€œ512,0â€, the @ref AVStreamGroupTileGrid.offsets â€œoffsetâ€ of the topleft pixel of the fifth @ref AVStreamGroup.streams â€œstreamâ€ in the group is â€œ0,512â€, the @ref AVStreamGroupTileGrid.offsets â€œoffsetâ€, of the topleft pixel of the sixth @ref AVStreamGroup.streams â€œstreamâ€ in the group is â€œ512,512â€, etc.

Assuming a canvas with size 1024x1024 and all tiles with a dimension of 512x512, a possible @ref AVStreamGroupTileGrid.offsets â€œoffsetâ€ for the topleft pixel of the first @ref AVStreamGroup.streams â€œstreamâ€ in the group would be 0x256, the @ref AVStreamGroupTileGrid.offsets â€œoffsetâ€ for the topleft pixel of the second @ref AVStreamGroup.streams â€œstreamâ€ in the group would be 256x512, the @ref AVStreamGroupTileGrid.offsets â€œoffsetâ€ for the topleft pixel of the third @ref AVStreamGroup.streams â€œstreamâ€ in the group would be 512x256, and the @ref AVStreamGroupTileGrid.offsets â€œoffsetâ€ for the topleft pixel of the fourth @ref AVStreamGroup.streams â€œstreamâ€ in the group would be 256x0.
